author: Kenny Douglass
title: Mater Dei beats Reitz 29-28
text:
Mater Dei beats Reitz 29-28 - Tri-State News, Weather & Sports Member Center: Mater Dei beats Reitz 29-28 Posted: kdouglass@14news.com EVANSVILLE, IN (WFIE) - 
12,962 fans packed the Reitz Bowl on Friday night to watch the Mater Dei Wildcats beat the Reitz Panthers, 29-28, for the City and SIAC Championships. 
Both teams went into the game with a score of 8 wins, 0 loses. 
Joe Downs and Bo McFall will have highlights from the game during Touchdown Live on 14NEWS at 10.
